      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.778 - He (Ali ibn Ja’far ) asked Him, Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as), about a musk pouch being with someone while they are praying, either in their pocket or clothing.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in that.\""
        ]
